Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: soc-pcm.c: tidyup playback/capture_only at soc_get_playback_capture()
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e1f653ce847bab7285dd135cabe3ce544e574c75
